{"tid":818843,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【颱風消息】膠紙是日最高價 炒到54蚊","createTime":"2018-09-14T11:20:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-14T11:24:38.000Z","uid":208748,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1da2df83c07dc38374edde7759bbd570b27338b0","tid":818843,"uid":208748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T11:20:40.000Z","msg":"颱風殺到，部份食腦嘅香港人，梗係又搵嘢嚟炒。今日中午開始，不斷流傳兩個消息，一個係iPhone炒唔起，另一個就係香港人已經轉炒膠紙。<br />\n<br />\n封窗膠紙嘅最新報價，填詞人梁栢堅中午過後已經出post，話有舗頭由早上10蚊炒到29蚊，點知原來仲有得升，最新報價，有舖頭疑似已經炒到54蚊﹗<br />\n<br />\n膠紙呢啲生活必需品，平時供求都唔會特別增加，如今短時間內淘寶都淘唔切，自然好炒。同埋呢啲邊有收市，隨時長升長有⋯⋯素來有獅子山下精神嘅香港人，真係識得「捉緊機遇」。<br />\n<br />\n之不過，今次颱風真係唔係講笑，睇怕無論點貴，大家都要「硬食」買膠紙封窗㗎啦。<br />\n（不斷更新：截至17：45最高報價：80蚊）<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E3%80%90%E9%A2%B1%E9%A2%A8%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF%E3%80%91%E8%86%A0%E7%B4%99%E6%98%AF%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%80%E9%AB%98%E5%83%B9-%E7%82%92%E5%88%B054%E8%9A%8A-093335944.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E9%25A2%25B1%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E6%25B6%2588%25E6%2581%25AF%25E3%2580%2591%25E8%2586%25A0%25E7%25B4%2599%25E6%2598%25AF%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%2580%25E9%25AB%2598%25E5%2583%25B9-%25E7%2582%2592%25E5%2588%25B054%25E8%259A%258A-093335944.html&d=Z%2FX2r%2BYHNENfykGPwY00Y5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=b9bb8c45\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E3%80%90%E9%A2%B1%E9%A2%A8%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF%E3%80%91%E8%86%A0%E7%B4%99%E6%98%AF%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%80%E9%AB%98%E5%83%B9-%E7%82%92%E5%88%B054%E8%9A%8A-093335944.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nCLS香港真係咩都有得炒"},{"pid":"34bf5992ac9198d3c30006d169d1e2d05d1d1b2a","tid":818843,"uid":107231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T11:21:35.000Z","msg":"On9 先會痴窗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"782ea1b56fd1c844